body:
#Hello world ##What is your name ###Possible names include * Bob * John * Jill * Anna ###Quotes about names > If you can't answer a man's arguments, all is not lost; you can still call him vile names. > -Elbert Hubbard ###Some names are better than others ####Names can be ranked If you like HTML
NameAwesomeness (out of 10)
Bob5
John7
Jill2
Anna9
##Stuff about me ###My favorite websites 1. I like [robots] [1]. Our robotics team has **a lot** of [divisions][]. 2. I also like [journalism](http://elestoque.org "El Estoque"). My *favorite* section is sports. [1]: http://mvrt.com/?eltoro "El Toro" [divisions]: http://mvrt.com/?divisions "Divisions" ###Things I like Lines *** Yay! Do you like the `println()` function? It prints things prettily, like this big flower ![Flower and butterfly](http://www.sxc.hu/pic/m/j/ja/jarnek/1425538_the_butterfly.jpg "Yay flowers")
